defaultQ1 default&#xa0; 
defaultChair:default Good morning and welcome.  I should explain that in the temporary absence of one of our witnesses, we took the opportunity to complete another piece of business, but now we have the complete team here, so we can start.  Can I welcome you and thank you for agreeing to give evidence at this inquiry?  Just before we start the questioning, if you could introduce yourselves for voice transcription purposes that would be very helpful.
default&#xa0;
defaultToni Pearcedefault: Hi, I am Toni; I am the President of the National 
defaultUnion
default of Students.
defaultBahram Bekhradniadefault: I am Bahram
