default&#x2011;
defaultcollection tactics is of course acceptable, but I have asked the question several times about how this would be done and whether we have an idea of how these private companies work and what their ethic is and what their values are.  In fact, they are acting on behalf of Government when they collect these debts, whether that loan has been sold or not.
