default,
default private or public providers operate in the market—even looking at quality and how you ensure the protection of students if it does not work out with a provider?  How do you ensure that quality is provided at an institution?  What we have seen is that there have been no steps to support those students, and we then end up with this kind of black hole in finances, where for
default&#x2011;
